### ==================== ADMIN STATISTICS ====================

### Get Overview Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/overview HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Revenue Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/revenue HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Order Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/orders HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Product Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/products HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get User Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/users HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Top Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/statistics/top-products?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ==================== ADMIN USER MANAGEMENT ====================

### Get All Users (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update User Information
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "hoTen": "Nguyen Van B",
    "email": "user.updated@example.com",
    "soDienThoai": "0987654321",
    "diaChi": "123 Updated Address, Ho Chi Minh City",
    "vaiTro": "khach_hang"
}

###

### Lock/Unlock User Account
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/5/lock HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/users/5 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ==================== ADMIN ORDER MANAGEMENT ====================

### Get All Orders (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Orders by Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders?page=0&size=10&status=dat_hang HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Order Detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders/1/status?status=da_giao HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update Order Information
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "trangThaiDonHang": "da_giao",
    "diaChiGiaoHang": "Updated delivery address",
    "soDienThoaiNhan": "0912345678",
    "ghiChu": "Delivered successfully"
}

###

### Delete Order
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/orders/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ==================== ADMIN VOUCHER MANAGEMENT ====================

### Get All Vouchers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Voucher Detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Create New Voucher
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "code": "SAVE20",
    "moTa": "Giảm giá 20% cho tất cả sản phẩm",
    "giaTriGiam": 20,
    "loaiGiam": "percent",
    "giaTriToiThieu": 500000,
    "giamToiDa": null,
    "ngayBatDau": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
    "ngayKetThuc": "2025-12-31T23:59:59",
    "soLuong": 100
}

###

### Create Another Voucher
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "code": "SAVE100K",
    "moTa": "Giảm giá 100,000 VND cho đơn hàng từ 1,000,000 VND",
    "giaTriGiam": 100000,
    "loaiGiam": "fixed",
    "giaTriToiThieu": 1000000,
    "giamToiDa": 100000,
    "ngayBatDau": "2025-01-15T00:00:00",
    "ngayKetThuc": "2025-03-31T23:59:59",
    "soLuong": 50
}

###

### Update Voucher
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "moTa": "Giảm giá 25% cho tất cả sản phẩm - cập nhật",
    "giaTriGiam": 25,
    "soLuong": 150
}

###

### Delete Voucher
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/vouchers/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ==================== ADMIN REVIEW MANAGEMENT ====================

### Get All Reviews (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/reviews?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Approve Review
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/reviews/1/approve HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Reject Review
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/reviews/2/reject HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Delete Review
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/reviews/3 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ==================== ADMIN SYSTEM CONFIGURATION ====================

### Get System Configuration
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/system-config HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update System Configuration
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/system-config HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "appName": "StepUp Shoes",
    "appVersion": "1.0.1",
    "maxUploadSize": "20MB",
    "sessionTimeout": "60 minutes"
}

###

### ==================== ADMIN ACTIVITY LOGS ====================

### Get Activity Logs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/activity-logs?page=0&size=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

